data.description: Great home on a corner lot. Large front covered porch with a large front yard. Front door opens to a living room and kitchen. Fireplace in the living room. Nice open concept. Large laundry room off the living room. 3 bedroom and bathroom down the hall. Primary bedroom includes a bathroom. Large second bathroom with a walk in shower. Large backyard with a pool and cover patio. The seller has left several bottle of chemicals for the pool and the pool toys. What is left in the home conveys. Roof is 6 years old. The home comes as is, the owner will not do any repairs.
